{
  "stem": "740.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was just a little, tiny powerhouse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Matter of fact, when I boxed for the Maccabi when I was about 12 years old, I weighed like 138 pounds.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was five foot two.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I looked like Popeye.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And yeah, I was a husky little guy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you said the wrong word to me and I popped away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I got into all kinds of problems.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The teachers would call my father if he was home or would call my mother, and all kinds of headaches.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But politically, as a youngster, you don't know what's going.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, today, people tell me, oh, I remember when I was five years old.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were-- this is nonsense.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When you're seven and eight years old, all you're interested in is play around, do dumb things, get into mischief.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You don't know what's going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But as you grow up in the city where there's so much noise-- and Berlin was a noisy city, a big city.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The Olympics were on, so you could see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By that time already, the movement started to harass the Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had benches in the parks which said 'Jews, Negroes, and dogs not allowed.' You had the public swimming pools, 'Jews, Negroes, and Dogs not allowed.' Or you had public bathrooms, and it said, 'For Aryans only,' which in my studies later on, is a joke, because an Aryan-- a German is never an Aryan.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The true Aryans are the Hindus.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where he ever got the name from, who knows?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you could see the dark clouds coming on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And even as a youngster, you began to notice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the boys you played with when you were five, six, and seven, they wore Hitler uniforms.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They wore [GERMAN] uniforms.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
